?userid=2858989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552052059" alt="Westrin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2858989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" >Westrin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drannoyingdog" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2425082&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552052059" alt="DrAnnoyingDog" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2425082)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drannoyingdog" >DrAnnoyingDog</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/janitorcakeworth" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3484414&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552052059" alt="JanitorCakeworth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3484414)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/janitorcakeworth" >JanitorCakeworth</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552052059" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grimcreeper" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2523494&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1552052059" alt="GrimCreeper" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2523494)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grimcreeper" >GrimCreeper</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php